
  <sn><md>#### Type : Basic Concepts of Percentage {.text-center}

**Key Formulas**

* **x is what percent of y?**
  $$
  \frac{x}{y} \times 100%
  $$
  ![diagram](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Nh-em0n/QDoc/main/BCS/Math/03.Percentage/media/dg0.svg)

* **p% of q?**
  $$
  q \times \frac{p}{100}
  $$

  **Example:** What is 10% of 80?
  $$
  80 \times \frac{10}{100} = 8
  $$

* **x is what percent greater than y?**
  $$
  \frac{x - y}{y} \times 100%
  $$
  ![diagram](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Nh-em0n/QDoc/main/BCS/Math/03.Percentage/media/dg2.svg)
* **x is what percent lesser than y?**
  $$
  \frac{y - x}{y} \times 100%
  $$
</md></sn>
